			<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/global-opinions/how-instability-in-the-middle-east-could-affect-trumps-reelection-bid/2020/03/03/9c9e7ee4-5d86-11ea-9055-5fa12981bbbf_story.html" class="written">Institute expert quoted by the Washington Post on the Trump peace plan's consequences for Jordan.</a>
		</p>
		<p class="close">
<cite><a  href="https://www.washingtoninstitute.org/experts/view/satloff-robert" >Robert Satloff</a></cite>
</p>
